org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.grouping.functions

Class TransposeVertexGroupItems

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.grouping.functions.TransposeVertexGroupItems
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, org.apache.flink.api.common.functions.Function, org.apache.flink.api.common.functions.GroupReduceFunction<VertexGroupItem,org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple2<VertexGroupItem,IdWithIdSet>>

    public class TransposeVertexGroupItems
extends Object
implements org.apache.flink.api.common.functions.GroupReduceFunction<VertexGroupItem,org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple2<VertexGroupItem,IdWithIdSet>>
    Takes a group of VertexGroupItem as input where each item represents the same group but stores a unique super vertex ids. This function creates a single VertexGroupItem that represents the whole group and also outputs a set containing all the super vertex ids of the incoming items. Example input: (1,A) (2,A) (3,B) (4,B) Example output: ((10,A),(10,[1,2])) ((20,B),(20,[3,4]))
